greene lyon group inc private company information  bloomberg july    pm et metals and mining company overview of greene lyon group inc snapshot people company overview greene lyon group inc develops and licenses technologies focused primarily on recycling precious metals pm from scrap materials and industrial byproducts generated across multiple industries its portfolio includes pm and pm technologies for recycling precious metals from a range of base metal substrates tf a nonchemical process that uses a specific dielectric fluid in a proprietary application to recover chips from populated circuit boards for secure data destruction for reuse or as a first step to refine the precious metals in the chips and pbl technology for recovering lead and glass from cathode ray tubes found in old tvs and computer monitors the company was incorporated  greene lyon group inc develops and licenses technologies focused primarily on recycling precious metals pm from scrap materials and industrial byproducts generated across multiple industries its portfolio includes pm and pm technologies for recycling precious metals from a range of base metal substrates tf a nonchemical process that uses a specific dielectric fluid in a proprietary application to recover chips from populated circuit boards for secure data destruction for reuse or as a first step to refine the precious metals in the chips and pbl technology for recovering lead and glass from cathode ray tubes found in old tvs and computer monitors the company was incorporated in  and is based in beverly massachusetts with a laboratory in quebec canada detailed description  cummings centersuite pbeverly ma united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwgreenelyoncom key executives for greene lyon group inc mr dale r johnson chief executive officer and president mr john walshe vice president of operations dr svitlana moskovchenko chief technology officer compensation as of fiscal year  similar private companies by industry company name reg