quids we also have available to us a hitachi scanning electron microscope tm a retsch planetary ball mill and a retsch sm grinder we are planning to acquire additional specialized equipment and lab technicians in  to expand and accelerate our rd activitiesgreene lyon canada inc boul cartier ouestsuite laval qc hv bcanada company namegreene lyon group incbusiness categoryscrap metal recyclingaddress cummings center suite pbeverlymassachusettsunited stateszip presidentdale r johnsonyear establishedemployeesnamembershipsnahours of operationnacompany servicesprecious metal refiningchip recoverycrt recyclingtechnologies in development contact detailskey contactsshareholderssubsidiariesphone numberlocked contentsubscribe to viewfax numberlocked contentemaillocked contentwebsitelocked contentnamepositioncontact detailssubscribe to viewpresidentlocked contentvp operationslocked contentpresidentlocked contentchief technology officerlocked content not available not availablecompany review start your review of greene lyon group inc submit reviewscrap metal recycling companies crusher incwest chicagounited states phibrotech incteaneckunited states metallico krieger recycling associatesrochesterunited statesking auto group rockleaaustraliacashforcarsbrisbanerockleaaustraliacompanies in united stateskeymark enterprisesbouldercoloradounited states premier energy services llccolumbiamarylandunited stateskelly klosure systemsfremontnew hampshireunited states williams engineering ltdminneapolisminnesotaunited states progressive engineering  desigfort washingtonpennsylvaniaunited states is this your company claim this listingwrong information submit correctionsadd to favoritescontact company your name your email phone number your message i would like to recieve periodic email updates from scrapmonster send messageby continuing you agree to the terms  conditions and privacy policy of this website location map × submit corrections your name your email phone number describe your changesc