 help mitigate the negative environmental consequences of global growth we will create value for our shareholders build a legacy we can be proud of and have fun our visiongreene lyon group will be a premier provider of sustainable precious metal recycling technologies for a wide range of materials across multiple industries and will be a leader in the global transition to a circular economy and sustainable materials management home page rotatorour missionat greene lyon group our mission is to develop new technologies for recycling precious metals that are cheaper faster and more sustainable than the conventional methods they replacehttpsitegreenelyonamherstpartnersnetimagesbannershomepageerecoveryjpgour technologies will make it economically compelling to recycle precious metals in an environmentally responsible manner and thereby help mitigate the negative environmental consequences of global growth we will create value for our shareholders build a legacy we can be proud of and have funhttpsitegreenelyonamherstpartnersnetimagesbannershomepageewastejpgour visiongreene lyon group will be a premier provider of sustainable precious metal recycling technologies for a wide range of materials across multiple industries and will be a leader in the global transition to a circular economy and sustainable materials managementhttpsitegreenelyonamherstpartnersnetimagesbannershomepageewastejpg welcome to greene lyon group we develop and commercialize proprietary technologies focused primarily on recycling gold silver and other precious metals pm from scrap materials and industrial byproducts our technologies are cheaper faster and more sustainable than the conventional pm recovery methods they replace our goal is to build a robust portfolio of superior pm recycling technologies for a wide range of materials across multiple industries we are headquartered in beverly massachusetts with an rd laboratory in laval quebec read more our laboratory check out greene lyon groups laborator